ai_summary.en: The crypto market is currently entrenched in "Extreme Fear" with the BTC Fear & Greed Index at 22. Despite this, institutional whales on Ethereum, while active with high neutral volume, maintain a largely neutral sentiment and zero stablecoin net flow, suggesting cautious rebalancing rather than strong directional bets. Conversely, speculative whales on Solana exhibit a slightly more bearish stance, characterized by much lower volume and a notable outflow of stablecoins, indicating de-risking. This divergence suggests institutional caution amid retail capitulation, pointing to continued market uncertainty with potential downside pressure, especially on more speculative chains.
ai_summary.zh: 加密市场目前陷入“极度恐惧”，比特币恐惧与贪婪指数为22。尽管如此，以太坊上的机构巨鲸虽然交易量大且方向不明朗，但情绪基本中性，稳定币净流量为零，表明更多是谨慎的再平衡而非明确的方向性押注。相比之下，Solana上的投机性巨鲸则表现出略微悲观的情绪，其交易量远低于以太坊，且有显著的稳定币流出，预示着风险规避。这种分歧表明在散户投降之际机构保持谨慎，预示市场将持续不确定性，特别是在更具投机性的链上，可能面临进一步的下行压力。
